flags in linestr:

 * font at line start (8 bits)
 * Ipicture(s) on this line
 * L/Rpicture on this line but this is not start
 * Start of line is in cross ref
 * start of line is in local def
 * local def on this line
 * cross ref on this line

Other bits:

 * left margin (inc picture skip)
 * width (accounting for picture skip)
 * offset to text
